Short Description: In today's ultra-competitive market it is critical that dentists have a clear & constant view of the business in their practice. The sad truth is that many practitioners are not making what they would like & they don't seem to know why? This 2-day seminar will take dentists through a comprehensive analysis of the metrics & processes employed by dental practices that are profitable in any economy. Dentists will leave this course with actionable items they can start implementing Monday morning.Read More
